snippet.title: Best VGM 535 - Shenmue - Shenhua (Dreamcast's 10th Anniversary)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 301 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_OguBY5x-Qo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Dreamcast
Shenmue (2000)
Shenhua
Ryuji Iuchi
